},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"我知呀<br />\n所以就係話超過56個民族存在<br />\n因為所謂「漢族」同「中華民族」一樣係騙局"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"漢族先係最大騙局<br />\n語言 習俗 飲食 血源 體格 樣貌 差天共地都叫同一民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d286b7936162e04b653a5c7d90f0fb978c1cbf7","tid":1902071,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣正名獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滿洲獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南蒙古自行獨立或與北蒙古組成聯邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圖博獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n東突厥獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fbe239232b664f3caa37e546e193e177bfe45d","tid":1902071,"uid":38570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42ce3316c6dcb6a99aacc62bf811f7424ab0cc16","tid":1902071,"uid":306337,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"好老實講, 其實我覺得我地同台灣先係真正嘅中華民族後裔, 嗰班支那人不過係偷鳩咗我地個名同我地嘅國家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"唔好加個地字<br />\n你條中國賤種唔好諗住拉埋香港人落水"},{"pid":"57f0e842701df37852fe651628cf351388f9346a","tid":1902071,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75fbe239232b664f3caa37e546e193e177bfe45d","tid":1902071,"uid":38570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42ce3316c6dcb6a99aacc62bf811f7424ab0cc16","tid":1902071,"uid":306337,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"好老實講, 其實我覺得我地同台灣先係真正嘅中華民族後裔, 嗰班支那人不過係偷鳩咗我地個名同我地嘅國家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"唔好加個地字<br />\n你條中國賤種唔好諗住拉埋香港人落水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁係咪要行去中華化?